Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够
